  "description": [
    "Romnul American THE ROMANIAN AMERICAN Published by The Romanian American Publishing Association Incorporated Entered as Second Class Matter at the Post Office at Detroit Michigan under the Act of March 3 1879 Edited by a Committee PUBLISHED WEEKLY MARIA MILA Business Manager Costul Abonamentului In Statele Unite pe an 400 pe 6 luni 300 In Strln\u0103tate pe an 500 pe 6 luni 400 de lug C BORDEIANU Ogoarele proasp\u0103t \u00eens\u0103m\u00een \u0163ate ca \u015fi p\u0103\u015funile \u015fi f\u00eene\u0163ele de jos cum le spun \u0163\u0103ranii muncitori din comuna S\u0103li\u015fte raionul Sibiu se \u00eentind p\u00een\u0103 sub poalele mun\u0163ilor la mar ginea p\u0103durilor de brazi \u015fi fagi Cu ani \u00een urm\u0103 zeci de hec tare din p\u0103\u015funile de munte e rau n\u0103p\u0103dite de l\u0103st\u0103ri\u015furi d\u0103 un\u0103toare care sc\u0103deau supra fa\u0163a bun\u0103 de p\u0103\u015funat In toamna anului 1949 au ve nit la S\u0103li\u015fte ingineri trimi\u015fi de Ministerul Agriculturii Ei au \u00eenceput s\u0103 m\u0103soare p\u0103\u015funea \u00een lung \u015fin lat Apoi nu dup\u0103 mult timp la gar\u0103 au sosit mii de metri de s\u00eerm\u0103 Oamenii erau nedumeri\u0163i Ei nu pricepeau \u00eenc\u0103 rostul noilor \u00eentocmiri de care li se vorbea C\u00eend sa dus \u00eens\u0103 vestea c\u0103 trebuie oameni la amenajarea p\u0103\u015funii din Santa mul\u0163i au \u00een ceput s\u0103 urce"
  ],
